Package edu.baylor.GroupFive.database.daos

Class BaseDAO<T>

java.lang.Object
edu.baylor.GroupFive.database.daos.BaseDAO<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
RoomDAO, TransactionDAO, UserDAO
public abstract class BaseDAO<T> extends Object
This class is an abstract class that represents the base functionalities for all *DAO objects in our project. We allow the user to retrieve a connection to our database along with the following functionality: get(int) getAll() save(Object) insert(Object) update(Object) delete(Object)
Author:
Brendon, Cole
